1. Definitions

For the purposes of this License:

"Nyx VM" refers to the Nyx Virtual Machine runtime software,
including all components contained within the `nyx-vm` package.

"Software" refers to the Nyx VM and all associated materials including,
but not limited to:

• source code
• compiled binaries
• runtime implementations
• bytecode execution engines
• documentation
• architecture and internal implementation details
• build scripts and configuration files
• test suites and examples

"Author" refers to Surya Sekhar Roy.

